txt.en: Orc soldiers can be found in Arandor.\n\nYou should defeat Orc soldiers and lieutenants.
A bounty asks you to thin the Orc numbers and slay their lieutenants in Arandor.

You defeated Orc lieutenants and successfully thinned the ranks of the Orc soldiers. The man who posted the bounty must be pleased, but you do wonder how many potential bounty-seekers his notice may have sent into danger.

The bounty notice reads:\n\n'Pay attention to this notice! Do not assume one of your brethren will heed it! Yes, I am writing this to you! The Orcs' numbers are getting out of control in Arandor, and a group of their lieutenants has been rallying for an assault on our camp. Put an end to it, and you will be handsomely rewarded. Yes, you!'
